user.description: Username displayed above the review description, at the right of the icon

description.description: Review description displayed below the review username, at the top of the rate

url.description: Review external url. If set, an icon will be displayed at the top right of the review

logo.description: Top icon, displayed at the top right of the container. If not provided, a default icon is displayed (if an url is provided too)

max.description: max vote (max number of icons displayed) - extended from [Rater component](../../atoms/Rater/props.md#max)
max.comment: max vote (max number of icons displayed) - extended from {@link https://cianciarusocataldo.github.io/mobrix-ui/components/atoms/Rater Rater}

vertical.description: if `true`, rate icons will be displayed vertically - extended from [Rater component](../../atoms/Rater/props.md#vertical)
vertical.comment: if `true`, rate icons will be displayed vertically - extended from {@link https://cianciarusocataldo.github.io/mobrix-ui/components/atoms/Rater Rater}

emptyIcon.description: Empty rate icon, used to render the rate value. If not set, a standard unfilled star icon is used - extended from [Rater component](../../atoms/Rater/props.md#emptyIcon)
emptyIcon.comment: Empty rate icon, used to render the rate value. If not set, a standard unfilled star icon is used - extended from {@link https://cianciarusocataldo.github.io/mobrix-ui/components/atoms/Rater Rater}

fullIcon.description: Full rate icon, used to render the rate value. If not set, a standard filled star icon is used - extended from [Rater component](../../atoms/Rater/props.md#fullIcon)
fullIcon.comment: Full rate icon, used to render the rate value. If not set, a standard filled star icon is used - extended from {@link https://cianciarusocataldo.github.io/mobrix-ui/components/atoms/Rater Rater}
